Welcome to Verse Vanish
# Verse Vanish - Song Lyrics App

Verse Vanish is a web application built using JavaScript and React that allows users to explore and retrieve random song verses from a selection of songs. It utilizes React Bootstrap for styling, Axios for making API requests, and Node.js for backend functionality.

## Table of Contents
- [Features](#features)
- [Installation](#installation)
- [Usage](#usage)
- [API](#api)
- [Contributing](#contributing)
- [License](#license)

## Features

- Retrieve random song verses from a curated collection of songs.
- User-friendly interface built with React Bootstrap components.
- Seamless communication with the song lyrics API using Axios.
- Node.js backend for handling API requests and data manipulation.

## Installation

1. Clone this repository to your local machine using:

2. Navigate to the project directory:

3. Install the required dependencies for both the frontend and backend:

The backend server will be running on port 3000 by default, serving API requests for retrieving song verses.

## API

The backend of the Verse Vanish app uses an API to fetch song verses. The API endpoint is exposed at `/api/verse/:song`.

- `GET /api/verse/:song`:
Retrieves a random verse from the specified song in the collection.

